A '''wank''' was a creature found on the [[Endor/Legends|Forest Moon of Endor]]. It had [[Eye/Legends|eyes]] that could be dried and used in [[Magic/Legends|magical]] concoctions. [[Gonster]] used dried wank's eyes in the creation of the [[magic cap]], a magical hat that was used to trap the [[Raich]] in the form of a harmless tree.

